---
// Un formulario limpio, pidiendo solo lo esencial para que convierta mejor.
---

<section id="demo" class="py-20 bg-slate-50 relative">
  <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand-light to-transparent"></div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-brand-dark/5 border border-brand-light/50 overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row">
      
      <div class="bg-brand-blue p-10 md:w-5/12 text-white flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-brand-green/20 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
        
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 relative z-10">Solicita tu demostración gratuita</h3>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-6 relative z-10">Déjanos tus datos y un especialista de Rapidgest te enseñará la plataforma en menos de 24 horas.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 relative z-10">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/90">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Sin compromiso
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/90">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Configuración guiada
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-10 md:w-7/12">
        <form class="space-y-5">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-brand-dark mb-1">Nombre</label>
              <input type="text" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-brand-light focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue focus:border-brand-blue outline-none transition-all" placeholder="Tu nombre">
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-brand-dark mb-1">Empresa</label>
              <input type="text" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-brand-light focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue focus:border-brand-blue outline-none transition-all" placeholder="Nombre empresa">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-brand-dark mb-1">Email profesional</label>
            <input type="email" class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-brand-light focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue focus:border-brand-blue outline-none transition-all" placeholder="hola@empresa.com">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-brand-blue hover:bg-brand-blue-hover text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 mt-2">
            Solicitar Demo Ahora
          </button>
          <p class="text-xs text-brand-dark/50 text-center mt-4">Al enviar este formulario aceptas nuestra política de privacidad.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>